\n沽空就沽空，乜撚嘢做空<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055f59986851134a3de6e4572ae7a5fea6355fb6","tid":2197291,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"智通財經APP獲悉，9月10日，沽空機構Hindenburg Research發佈電動卡車製造商Nikola Corp (NASDAQ:NKLA)的做空報告。<br />\n<br />\nHindenburg Research在報告中揭示了爲什麼他們相信Nikola是一個錯綜複雜的騙局，其建立在其創始人和執行董事長特雷弗&middot;米爾頓(Trevor Milton)職業生涯中的幾十個謊言之上。<br />\n<br />\n消息公佈後，Nikola股價迅速下跌，截至北京時間22:22，該股跌3.87%，報40.73美元。<br />\n<br />\n通過包括電話錄音、短信、私人電子郵件和幕後照片的大量證據，Hindenburg Research認爲公司在其半掛式卡車、電池技術、氫氣生產、Nikola One甚至其數十億美元大訂單等諸多方面存在數十個虛假聲明。<br />\n<br />\nHindenburg Research稱，其創始人將這些虛假聲明轉化爲一家市值約200億美元的上市公司，通過謊稱擁有大量專利技術來誤導合作伙伴簽署協議。他與世界上一些頂尖的汽車公司簽訂了合作協議，這些公司都急於追趕特斯拉(<a href=\"http://TSLA.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTSLA.US&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=0780a1e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">TSLA.US</a>)在電動汽車界的領導地位。該機構認爲Nikola的合作伙伴沒有做足功課。"},{"pid":"c96cecd270fe1620889e505b9f8dde5d1bebbfdf","tid":2197291,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7d2a796355a7ff9f5e3162b3d12e36550f537ab","tid":2197291,"uid":117318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"012188a5648efd755ec9b705914de3d9860f1241","tid":2197291,"uid":13193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af7eeb341f357e10718c79a81fda9fccd556b02d","tid":2197291,"uid":65928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"咁應該叫咩 沽空？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"基本啦<br />\n沽空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n看多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />看空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />財報<img src=\"/assets/